public interface Ordered
Interface for objects that are ordered.

Provides a programmatic alternative to Order.

Note that this interface only applies to injected collection types since the beans have to be instantiated to resolve the order therefore unlike Order it cannot be used for the purposes of prioritizing bean selection.

Since:
1.0
Author:
Graeme Rocher
